entries.s_24: A trader named Saun Dann is missing a shipment of his.
entries.s_26: Saun Dann you say? Let me check my files. Yes, that shipment came through here a couple of days ago. It was shipped to the Mos Entha starport on a backwater planet named Tatooine.
entries.s_40: A busy time around here I'm afraid. You're going to have to move along.
